org.osate.aadl2

Interface PropertySet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, ModelUnit, NamedElement, Namespace, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PropertySetImpl

    public interface PropertySet
extends Namespace, ModelUnit
    A representation of the model object 'Property Set'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owned Property Type
    • Owned Property
    • Owned Property Constant
    • Imported Unit

    See Also:
